            <title>[GROOVY-11751] VerifyError on indexed for loop</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-11751</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When the index of a for loop is captured by a closure, it causes a VerifyError.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;(i, v in []){println i}()&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error contents:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
